ttype - Variable in class java.io.StreamTokenizer
Contains the type of the token read resulting from a call to nextToken The rules are as follows: For a token consisting of a single ordinary character, this is the value of that character. For a quoted string, this is the value of the quote character For a word, this is TT_WORD For a number, this is TT_NUMBER For the end of the line, this is TT_EOL For the end of the stream, this is TT_EOF
